<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Page introuvable — AkiCloud</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy-950: #080e1c;
            --blue: #006eff;
            --blue-hover: #0059d4;
            --blue-shadow: rgba(0,110,255,.28);
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --text: #151d32;
            --text-2: #5c6484;
            --orange: #e67700;
            --orange-bg: #fff4e5;
            --r-sm: 6px;
            --r-lg: 14px;
            --shadow-lg: 0 12px 36px rgba(15,25,50,.14), 0 4px 10px rgba(15,25,50,.07);
            --t: all .16s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
            --font: 'Sora', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        }
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: var(--font);
            background: var(--navy-950);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        .error-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: var(--r-lg);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            padding: 48px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 420px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .error-icon {
            width: 64px; height: 64px;
            background: var(--orange-bg);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--orange);
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .error-desc {
            font-size: 13.5px;
            color: var(--text-2);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .btn-back {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 7px;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            background: var(--blue);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--r-sm);
            font-size: 13.5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: var(--font);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--t);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-back:hover {
            background: var(--blue-hover);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px var(--blue-shadow);
        }
        .btn-back i { font-size: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-card">
        <div class="error-icon"><i class="bi bi-search"></i></div>
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Page introuvable</h1>
        <p class="error-desc">La page que vous recherchez n'existe pas ou a été déplacée. Vérifiez l'URL ou retournez au tableau de bord.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-back"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>Retour au dashboard</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
